CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 2, 1957, pg. B6 reads: "Ivy Leafs - These proud young ladies are the new members of the Iota Chapter of Alpha Kappa Alpha Sorority's Ivy Leaf Club on the University of Pittsburgh's campus. Seated, left to right: Andrea Jones and Louella Blow.  Standing: Toni Holmes. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of new members of Alpha Kappa Alpha Sorority's Ivy Leaf Club; Andrea Jones, Toni Holmes, and Louella Blow, posed in interior with floral curtain
